skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: doctor finder
des:
Doctor Finder is a skill which can help you locate doctors in your area. This skill uses your device location to locate the doctors nearest to you as accurately as possible. You can specify the type of doctor you need and Doctor finder will give you their names. You are also provided with an option to get the doctors rating and address. You can say help to get more information about this skills functionality.

DISCLAIMER 
This tool does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
